# AI Medical Diagnosis Assistant - Multi-Agent System
# ===================================================
# Choose one provider (Anthropic recommended for multi-agent mode):

# Anthropic API (Recommended - powers the multi-agent system)
# Get your key from: https://console.anthropic.com/settings/keys
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-your-api-key-here

# OpenAI API (Legacy fallback)
# Get your key from: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-your-api-key-here

# Instructions:
# 1. Copy this file and rename it to .env
# 2. Set your Anthropic API key above
# 3. Restart the backend server: uvicorn main:app --reload
